{
  "stem": "323.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had to serve breakfast and dinner, and I had the whole day to ski.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I babysat at night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at this time, I came back to New York with over $1,200.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was a lot of money then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What did you do when you came back?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went back to school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I was contacted by this family in New Rochelle.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The mother needed some-- and I don't even recall what the operation was-- but she needed some sort of operation.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she asked me, would I stay and take care of the house and her two children when she was gone?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm hm.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had known someone in my family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's how I got to them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were paying me a very good salary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And besides that, and I had-- they hired someone to live in the attic, so I could go to school at night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I could-- I didn't have to be there at night.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was there for three months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then the young woman who lived up on the top floor was the secretary of Maxwell Dane, who became my boss for my first job, for Doyle Dane Bernbach.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was an advertising agency.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So this is how it all--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then when we-- when after the three months were up, I had to look for a place to live.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so this woman, Nell, said, well why don't we share an apartment?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we rented a two-bedroom apartment in New Rochelle and commuted to New York.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I started working at Doyle Dane Bernbach.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we were 14-- 16 people, I believe, including myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was like a-- I did everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was like that became my family.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
